/// Get an immutable borrow to the element at the specified index.
///
/// This function returns an immutable borrow to the element at the specified
/// `index` in the slice.
///
/// Bounds checking is performed. If an out of bounds access occurs, it aborts.
_Safe const T *borrow _Nonnull SliceMut<T>::get(This this, size_t index) {
